videos.description: Colorado State's J.D. Paige hits a 3-pointer in the corner, moving them within 3 of Nevada.

videos.description: After Nevada's Caleb Martin steals the ball, Cody Martin drives to the basket for a layup and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Martin makes layup after steal
